column1: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `BorrowedList` ( `borrow_id` INTEGER AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY , `user_id` INTEGER NOT NULL , `book_id` INTEGER NOT NULL , `borrow_date` DATE NOT NULL , `due_date` DATE NOT NULL , `return_date` DATE , `is_returned` BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE , FOREIGN KEY ( `user_id` ) REFERENCES SYSTEM_USER ( `userId` ) ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY ( `book_id` ) REFERENCES `Book` ( `id` ) ON DELETE CASCADE )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `Book` ( `id` INTEGER AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY , `title` VARCHARACTER (?) NOT NULL UNIQUE , TYPES VARCHARACTER (?) , `authors` VARCHARACTER (?) , `abstract` LONGTEXT , `languages` TEXT , `createdDate` DATE , `coverURL` VARCHARACTER (?) , `subjects` VARCHARACTER (?) , `isbns` VARCHARACTER (?) )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `Review` ( `reviewId` INTEGER AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY , `userId` INTEGER NOT NULL , `bookId` INTEGER NOT NULL , `content` VARCHARACTER (?) , `ratings` DECIMAL (...) , FOREIGN KEY ( `userId` ) REFERENCES SYSTEM_USER ( `userId` ) ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY ( `bookId` ) REFERENCES `Book` ( `id` ) ON DELETE CASCADE )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS SYSTEM_USER ( `userId` INTEGER AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY , `first_name` VARCHARACTER (?) , `last_name` VARCHARACTER (?) NOT NULL , `email` VARCHARACTER (?) NOT NULL UNIQUE , PASSWORD VARCHARACTER (?) NOT NULL , `fees_due` DECIMAL (...) DEFAULT ? , `user_type` CHARACTER (?) )
UPDATE `BorrowedList` SET `return_date` = ? , `is_returned` = TRUE WHERE `book_id` = ? AND `user_id` = ? AND `is_returned` = FALSE

SELECT `Review` . `ratings` , `Review` . `content` , `User` . `first_name` , `User` . `last_name` FROM `Review` JOIN SYSTEM_USER ON `Review` . `userId` = `User` . `userId` WHERE `Review` . `bookId` = ?
SELECT * FROM `BorrowedList` WHERE `book_id` = ? AND `user_id` = ? AND `is_returned` = FALSE
